    <h1 class="cordyceps-title">Neuroprotective Effects</h1>

    <p class="cordyceps-text">A study highlighted that <strong>Cordyceps militaris</strong> improves cognitive function and protects neurons against damage caused by oxidative stress, suggesting potential benefits in neurodegenerative conditions such as Alzheimer's and Parkinson's diseases.</p>

    <div class="section_image_div">
        <img class="section_image" src="content/section5_image.png" alt="Neuroprotective Effects">  
